        "json": "---\n\n**Classification:** UNCLASSIFIED // FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; **Policy Reference:** ESS FRAGO-6 &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; **Data Source:** Microsoft Defender for Endpoint via Microsoft Sentinel\n\nUse the **Time Range** selector and tabs below to explore each security domain. Status panels (pie charts + % tiles) use **fixed compliance windows** independent of the Time Range picker — changing the time range only affects trend charts and detail grids.",
